item.title: Big Rock
item.description: The blue marlin fishing tournament called The Big Rock is an exciting event each year in Eastern North Carolina. For the past 6 years I have used python to pull some interesting data from the website. In this post I display how.

item.title: Fake Business
item.description: A colleague and I collaborated on an AWS project to deepen our understanding of data engineering and to showcase some of our data science skills. We simulated a fake furniture company’s data to make it more realistc and fun.
